skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food genie
des:
Welcome to Food Genie!

 Not sure what to eat today or at you looking for something other than the same old same old? The Food Genie tell you what food and beverage holidays any day is.

Example:

- Ask The Food Genie what today is
- Ask The Food Genie what Saturday is

 * holiday information found on https://foodimentary.com/
